You're free to use the Kicad project, the schematics and the PCB layout in your personal, non-commercial purposes. Also, you can use the Gerber files to order copies of the PCB board.

Redistribution of the PCB board schematics or the Kicad project (files in the pcb directory) is not permitted without a written permission from the author.

If you want to use the PCB in commercial purposes, you're not allowed to do that without a written permission from the author. As an exception, making a small batch of boards, using some of the boards for personal projects and selling the remaining boards is permitted.


